{"tid":918739,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"原來香港3000 年前已有人住","createTime":"2018-11-27T12:44:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-27T13:13:07.000Z","uid":2403,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4ddfa64f44b8c2bd4e4c8f9faf55ad7319982b68","tid":918739,"uid":2403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T12:44:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港大多數古代石刻都瀕臨海濱，石壁石刻卻離開海岸約三百米。相信此處昔日也是海邊，其後海岸變遷始成今日之地貌。石刻紋飾由正方及圓形幾何紋構成，與古代青銅器上的圖案極相似。故此或可推斷，這石刻大約是青銅時代，即約三千年前，由本區先民所刻鑿。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amo.gov.hk/b5/monuments_05.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amo.gov.hk%2Fb5%2Fmonuments_05.php&d=MKIgJ7Rux3u9bR48ktVXaqNGKT0mDZcTD8WJHRevFdc%3D&h=4579215a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.amo.gov.hk/b5/monuments_05.php</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果香港獨立，咁香港國係咪有3000年歷史？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54748f2243a926a112e4bf916c65db6325516aec","tid":918739,"uid":7355,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:02:25.000Z","msg":"中國：自古以來....."},{"pid":"20bf164b007cac1a8ab22d7c013e3f9d7d7a4402","tid":918739,"uid":199016,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T13:13:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}